      <title>伦敦面临联合利华 170 亿欧元冰淇淋上市之战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/london-faces-battle-for-unilever-s-17-billion-ice-cream-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合利华公司(Unilever Plc)在伦敦和阿姆斯特丹之间启动了其170亿欧元（184亿美元）冰淇淋业务潜在上市的竞争，这增加了英国股市再次受挫的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/london-faces-battle-for-unilever-s-17-billion-ice-cream-listing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 12:37:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥迪首席财务官相信新款 Q6 E-Tron EV 将取得成功</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-19/audi-cfo-confident-new-q6-e-tron-ev-will-be-a-success-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国汽车制造商奥迪刚刚推出了其新电动车型 Q6 e-tron，首席财务官 Juergen Rittersberger 相信这款新电动汽车将在销售方面取得成功。但他对今年的电动汽车市场仍持谨慎态度。里特斯伯格在奥迪年度新闻发布会间隙与彭博社的奥利弗·克鲁克进行了交谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-19/audi-cfo-confident-new-q6-e-tron-ev-will-be-a-success-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 12:34:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油巨头称绿色转型进展缓慢</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-03-19/oil-chiefs-say-the-green-transition-is-falling-flat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚、沙特阿美和其他行业重量级企业的高管表示，尽管 ESG 运动不断涌现，但传统能源仍然充满生机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-03-19/oil-chiefs-say-the-green-transition-is-falling-flat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 12:29:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行首席执行官表示商业房地产将“缓慢燃烧”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/bofa-s-moynihan-says-commercial-real-estate-will-be-slow-burn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行首席执行官布赖恩·莫伊尼汉表示，在纽约一家地区银行就其问题债务风险向投资者发出警告后，银行业需要时间来解决商业房地产贷款问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/bofa-s-moynihan-says-commercial-real-estate-will-be-slow-burn</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 11:52:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
