    <item>
      <title>Astra 将以高达 24 亿美元的价格收购 Fusion Pharma</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/astrazeneca-to-buy-fusion-pharma-for-up-to-2-4-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧洲制药商继续大肆收购有前途的生物技术公司，阿斯利康公司 (AstraZeneca Plc) 同意以高达 24 亿美元的价格收购 Fusion Pharmaceuticals Inc.。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/astrazeneca-to-buy-fusion-pharma-for-up-to-2-4-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 07:17:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Calpers 加大对私募股权和信贷的押注，将 340 亿美元资金从股票转向投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/calpers-to-boost-private-assets-by-over-30-billion-move-away-from-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的养老基金正在加大对私募股权和私人信贷的投资，押注风险较高的资产将带来更高的回报，投资额达 340 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/calpers-to-boost-private-assets-by-over-30-billion-move-away-from-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 03:14:47 GMT</pubDate>
